{
  "video_id": "ttevamkS6gw",
  "title": "The Greater Insult",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 53880.0,
      "end_time": 55420.0,
      "text": "Marcus."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 55420.0,
      "end_time": 57400.0,
      "text": "Open your eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 59620.0,
      "end_time": 61620.0,
      "text": "Marcus: Where am I?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 61960.0,
      "end_time": 69820.0,
      "text": "You are about 27,000 light-years from Earth in the Sagittarius constellation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 69820.0,
      "end_time": 74740.0,
      "text": "on the outskirts of globular cluster NGC-6440,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 74740.0,
      "end_time": 76940.0,
      "text": "discovered by human beings"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 76940.0,
      "end_time": 79880.0,
      "text": "200 and 32 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 80880.0,
      "end_time": 82880.0,
      "text": "Turn around for a moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 84120.0,
      "end_time": 85360.0,
      "text": "and look up"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 87020.0,
      "end_time": 91480.0,
      "text": "There's single-celled life in the oceans of that planet up there."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 92140.0,
      "end_time": 96240.0,
      "text": "Life there will eventually become multicellular and terrestrial."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 97080.0,
      "end_time": 98280.0,
      "text": "Like on Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 98500.0,
      "end_time": 105060.0,
      "text": "over 99% of the species there will go extinct before one"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 105540.0,
      "end_time": 109960.0,
      "text": "finally makes it to where we are standing right now, on their moon."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 111020.0,
      "end_time": 112760.0,
      "text": "If I didn't want it that way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 113380.0,
      "end_time": 116320.0,
      "text": "then I would not have made it that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 117640.0,
      "end_time": 124660.0,
      "text": "Like a precious metal or jewel, for something to have value, it must be"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 125200.0,
      "end_time": 127000.0,
      "text": "finite."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 127000.0,
      "end_time": 129920.0,
      "text": "Nothing unlimited is precious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 130800.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132800.0,
      "text": "including life."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 134700.0,
      "end_time": 137580.0,
      "text": "Sabrina, open your eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 139000.0,
      "end_time": 140160.0,
      "text": "Sabrina: What's..."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 140160.0,
      "end_time": 141080.0,
      "text": "Sabrina: ...happening?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 141300.0,
      "end_time": 143560.0,
      "text": "Look at the horizon."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 144520.0,
      "end_time": 149740.0,
      "text": "You are about to see the sunrise of a red hypergiant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 150560.0,
      "end_time": 159700.0,
      "text": "and even though we're far from it, the scorched, desert world you're standing upon is 2,000 degrees Fahrenheit."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 160140.0,
      "end_time": 162140.0,
      "text": "Nothing lives here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 163160.0,
      "end_time": 169100.0,
      "text": "yet there are countless such places strewn about the universe like little motes of dust."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 170280.0,
      "end_time": 175400.0,
      "text": "Though this entire world is but a mote of dust, so, too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 175400.0,
      "end_time": 181900.0,
      "text": "is that red hypergiant when compared to the galaxy it calls home."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 183020.0,
      "end_time": 186880.0,
      "text": "And though that red hypergiant is but a mote of dust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 186880.0,
      "end_time": 189820.0,
      "text": "so, too, is that entire"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 190220.0,
      "end_time": 197680.0,
      "text": "galaxy, when compared to the cloud of galaxies in this tiny corner of the universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 198660.0,
      "end_time": 209080.0,
      "text": "I did not author such massive scale and variety for one type of people to think one type of way"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 211220.0,
      "end_time": 214640.0,
      "text": "Samuel, open your eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 216090.0,
      "end_time": 220000.0,
      "text": "I brought you to this place at random."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 220000.0,
      "end_time": 223360.0,
      "text": "We're in a galaxy far from the Milky Way."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 224180.0,
      "end_time": 227940.0,
      "text": "You did not know this place existed until you saw it."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 229040.0,
      "end_time": 234180.0,
      "text": "Space travels faster than the light that passes through it."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 234820.0,
      "end_time": 241480.0,
      "text": "As galaxies move farther apart, their light will eventually cease to reach each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 242360.0,
      "end_time": 247300.0,
      "text": "thus future civilizations, born long after Earth has disintegrated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 248560.0,
      "end_time": 251820.0,
      "text": "will know nothing of other galaxies."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 252520.0,
      "end_time": 255980.0,
      "text": "They'll know a universe of darkness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 256700.0,
      "end_time": 262380.0,
      "text": "but you, an organism born billions of years in their past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 262760.0,
      "end_time": 264760.0,
      "text": "totally shrouded by time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 265400.0,
      "end_time": 270660.0,
      "text": "have seen the beauty of a universe they will never know."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 296400.0,
      "end_time": 298960.0,
      "text": "I am the Lord your Godâ„¢"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 303200.0,
      "end_time": 311680.0,
      "text": "Throughout your lives I have watched your actions, heard your words, felt your emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 312920.0,
      "end_time": 322280.0,
      "text": "Sabrina, you were raised as a Muslim and have been a devout follower of Islam throughout your entire life."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 323080.0,
      "end_time": 324720.0,
      "text": "Please, rise."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 327940.0,
      "end_time": 340020.0,
      "text": "Marcus, you are a Christian, and though you aren't always steadfast, your faith grew as you got older, and when you died you were firm in your belief."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 340740.0,
      "end_time": 341900.0,
      "text": "Please,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 342060.0,
      "end_time": 342640.0,
      "text": "rise."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 345020.0,
      "end_time": 346120.0,
      "text": "Samuel."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 346360.0,
      "end_time": 351740.0,
      "text": "You were an atheist who was never convinced of my existence from the moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 351740.0,
      "end_time": 355580.0,
      "text": "you first heard about me right up until your death."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 357200.0,
      "end_time": 364480.0,
      "text": "Why have I gathered you three, of all people, here together after your deaths?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 367340.0,
      "end_time": 377989.0,
      "text": "You see, I was thinking of building a bar right over there, and I wanted to see what would happen when a Muslim a Christian and an atheist walked into it."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 381380.0,
      "end_time": 388020.0,
      "text": "[laughter]"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 388260.0,
      "end_time": 391080.0,
      "text": "Yeah, who wants to trade places with the atheist?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 396520.0,
      "end_time": 398340.0,
      "text": "You heard me."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 398440.0,
      "end_time": 403740.0,
      "text": "Look, your lives come with consequences, and you will be judged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 404380.0,
      "end_time": 406220.0,
      "text": "but, just this once,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 406220.0,
      "end_time": 411640.0,
      "text": "let us see if you're willing to trade places with this non-believer."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 411960.0,
      "end_time": 415120.0,
      "text": "Just step forward and raise your hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 415880.0,
      "end_time": 417880.0,
      "text": "Any takers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 422060.0,
      "end_time": 423740.0,
      "text": "I see."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 423740.0,
      "end_time": 425080.0,
      "text": "Very well."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 428640.0,
      "end_time": 429280.0,
      "text": "Samuel."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 432220.0,
      "end_time": 434380.0,
      "text": "I like you."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 435060.0,
      "end_time": 437220.0,
      "text": "Be at peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 439340.0,
      "end_time": 439840.0,
      "text": "[Mr. Darkmatter I don't feel so good]"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 440920.0,
      "end_time": 446820.0,
      "text": "You two on the other hand. Oh boy, do I have some words for you two."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 448620.0,
      "end_time": 449540.0,
      "text": "Get up!"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 450060.0,
      "end_time": 455220.0,
      "text": "That's your first problem. You think I want you kneeling before me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 455940.0,
      "end_time": 461620.0,
      "text": "What's worse: that you think I'm a monster, or that you don't realize you think I'm a monster?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 462600.0,
      "end_time": 468400.0,
      "text": "Why would I want people worshipping me? Is that what you would want out of your lives?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 469040.0,
      "end_time": 477700.0,
      "text": "Do you prefer equal, loving relationships, or for people to grovel before you with fear and reverence?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 477920.0,
      "end_time": 481600.0,
      "text": "Because, let me tell you, that gets old really fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 482360.0,
      "end_time": 491060.0,
      "text": "Every dictator who foolishly desired such power ended up being some of the loneliest people to ever live."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 492440.0,
      "end_time": 496540.0,
      "text": "Christians, Muslims, there's billions of you now."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 497160.0,
      "end_time": 501220.0,
      "text": "Billions! And you have so much fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 501880.0,
      "end_time": 508420.0,
      "text": "\"God-fearing\" is an actual phrase now, and it's supposed to be a good thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 509320.0,
      "end_time": 511060.0,
      "text": "Is that what you think I want?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 511400.0,
      "end_time": 512700.0,
      "text": "Fear?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 513380.0,
      "end_time": 515380.0,
      "text": "Sabrina, Marcus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 515780.0,
      "end_time": 522940.0,
      "text": "both of you actually believed that I send people to hell to be tortured."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 523400.0,
      "end_time": 524240.0,
      "text": "Tortured!"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 526100.0,
      "end_time": 531780.0,
      "text": "Sabrina, why would you worship someone who tortures people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 534480.0,
      "end_time": 537260.0,
      "text": "What choice did I have?"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 537340.0,
      "end_time": 548080.0,
      "text": "You can choose to have integrity and you can hope that your creator also has integrity."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 548280.0,
      "end_time": 554440.0,
      "text": "And if I am an enlightened being - and why wouldn't I be - then should I not also have integrity?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 555480.0,
      "end_time": 560100.0,
      "text": "Or you can trust those who claim to speak for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 561200.0,
      "end_time": 563860.0,
      "text": "It seems you have done the latter."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 565840.0,
      "end_time": 570540.0,
      "text": "Marcus, why would you worship someone who tortures people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 571480.0,
      "end_time": 576580.0,
      "text": "I-I-I just... I just trusted that you would know what's just."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 577260.0,
      "end_time": 579980.0,
      "text": "\"God is good, god is love.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 580660.0,
      "end_time": 582160.0,
      "text": "Love?"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 582420.0,
      "end_time": 588300.0,
      "text": "Since- since when does love have anything to do with inflicting agony for eternity?"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 589040.0,
      "end_time": 592420.0,
      "text": "You refused to take Sam's place"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 592780.0,
      "end_time": 599360.0,
      "text": "because Sam was an atheist. You believed Sam would go to hell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 600140.0,
      "end_time": 601280.0,
      "text": "didn't you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 604040.0,
      "end_time": 609860.0,
      "text": "And you trusted that sending Sam to hell would be justice?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 610820.0,
      "end_time": 615060.0,
      "text": "Sam merely didn't know that I exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 615780.0,
      "end_time": 621000.0,
      "text": "Should I feel insulted because of that? Should that offend me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 624960.0,
      "end_time": 626020.0,
      "text": "I-I don't know."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 626020.0,
      "end_time": 632700.0,
      "text": "Sam didn't know either of you exist, either. Do you feel insulted by that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 633980.0,
      "end_time": 634900.0,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 635060.0,
      "end_time": 639320.0,
      "text": "Yet, not only did both of you believe in me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 639620.0,
      "end_time": 644860.0,
      "text": "but both of you thought I was a monster who sends people to be tortured forever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 645120.0,
      "end_time": 649380.0,
      "text": "and desires the eternal worship of everyone else."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 649380.0,
      "end_time": 652380.0,
      "text": "I find that incredibly insulting."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 652380.0,
      "end_time": 654540.0,
      "text": "You offend me"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 655300.0,
      "end_time": 658560.0,
      "text": "Why would I want to be around someone like you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 659420.0,
      "end_time": 660620.0,
      "text": "Because..."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 660700.0,
      "end_time": 662600.0,
      "text": "We know better now."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 662600.0,
      "end_time": 663480.0,
      "text": "Do you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 663780.0,
      "end_time": 664580.0,
      "text": "Marcus: Yes!"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 665200.0,
      "end_time": 667540.0,
      "text": "How were we supposed to know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 668480.0,
      "end_time": 670940.0,
      "text": "Everyone around us believe these things."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 671760.0,
      "end_time": 677100.0,
      "text": "They were written thousands of years ago. Our churches, our friends, our"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 677640.0,
      "end_time": 680580.0,
      "text": "families, our whole society"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 681360.0,
      "end_time": 682920.0,
      "text": "believe these things."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 683080.0,
      "end_time": 684800.0,
      "text": "Samuel didn't."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 685220.0,
      "end_time": 689680.0,
      "text": "Even though he was alienated for it. He still didn't believe it."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 690600.0,
      "end_time": 697600.0,
      "text": "Throughout his life, he was the one who was called offensive and called out of line for not conforming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 697800.0,
      "end_time": 704060.0,
      "text": "sort of like Jesus was, yet it was the believers who offended me this whole time."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 704060.0,
      "end_time": 708540.0,
      "text": "It was the believers who nailed Jesus to the cross"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 709500.0,
      "end_time": 714100.0,
      "text": "You think those holy books weren't written by people just like you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 714320.0,
      "end_time": 715700.0,
      "text": "They ate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 715700.0,
      "end_time": 717600.0,
      "text": "drank, and slept"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 717760.0,
      "end_time": 718920.0,
      "text": "just like you."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 719440.0,
      "end_time": 725360.0,
      "text": "They had their ideas about what I'm like and they projected themselves onto me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 725360.0,
      "end_time": 729620.0,
      "text": "using me to justify their preferences, just like you."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 730420.0,
      "end_time": 735680.0,
      "text": "They used me to claim that their opinions were objective truths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 736420.0,
      "end_time": 739060.0,
      "text": "that their beliefs were knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 740360.0,
      "end_time": 743720.0,
      "text": "They didn't know where they ended and I began"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 744720.0,
      "end_time": 749720.0,
      "text": "You worshipped the god of the imaginations of ancient people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 750000.0,
      "end_time": 752260.0,
      "text": "who, not unlike the people of your time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 752320.0,
      "end_time": 756860.0,
      "text": "used their ideas of God to spread their influence"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 757100.0,
      "end_time": 762580.0,
      "text": "politically, culturally, and morally. You fell for it"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 763340.0,
      "end_time": 765780.0,
      "text": "Sabrina, you fell for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 766120.0,
      "end_time": 772080.0,
      "text": "Samuel did not. I can actually talk to Sam without all that baggage in the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 773060.0,
      "end_time": 778240.0,
      "text": "I can have a relationship with Sam I can be on equal footing with Sam."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 778520.0,
      "end_time": 782080.0,
      "text": "What am I supposed to do with you two?"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 782420.0,
      "end_time": 784060.0,
      "text": "Show us the truth!"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 784060.0,
      "end_time": 787980.0,
      "text": "Teach the truth to offensive cowards?"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 788260.0,
      "end_time": 791100.0,
      "text": "Have you not been irreparably damaged?"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 791300.0,
      "end_time": 791800.0,
      "text": "No!"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 791800.0,
      "end_time": 793040.0,
      "text": "We're not afraid of you!"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 796680.0,
      "end_time": 797200.0,
      "text": "Good."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 799000.0,
      "end_time": 801540.0,
      "text": "Now we're getting somewhere."
    }
  ]
}